ation-150\" href=\"/profile\">My Account</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/sell/new\">Post Free Ad</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-400 mb-4\">Features</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2.5\"><li><a class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/search?listingType=SELL\">Buy Vehicles</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/search?listingType=RENT\">Rent Vehicles</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/search?listingType=HIRE\">Hire Vehicle</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/auto-parts\">Auto Parts</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-400 mb-4\">Compare &amp; Tools</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2.5\"><li><a class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/compare\">Compare Ads</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/analyse\">Compare Models</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/profile?tab=favorites\">Saved Ads</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-400 mb-4\">Support</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2.5\"><li><a class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/about\">About Us</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/contact\">Contact Us</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/terms\">Terms of Services</a></li><li><a class=\"text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-teal-900/60 mt-8 pt-5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-2 text-xs text-slate-500\"><p>© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Rathagala.lk. All rights reserved.</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><a class=\"hover:text-slate-300 transition-colors\" href=\"/terms\">Terms</a><a class=\"hover:text-slate-300 transition-colors\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy</a><a class=\"hover:text-slate-300 transition-colors\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></div></div></div></footer></div></div><script>requestAnimationFrame(function(){$RT=performance.now()});</script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-ef7a5072982c10a2.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><div hidden id=\"S:0\"><div><section class=\"relative py-16 md:py-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-900 via-teal-800 to-teal-700 text-white overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden opacity-10\"><div class=\"absolute -right-40 -top-40 w-80 h-80 bg-teal-400 rounded-full\"></div><div class=\"absolute -left-20 bottom-10 w-60 h-60 bg-teal-300 rounded-full\"></div></div><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 font-heading\">About Rathagala.lk</h1><p class=\"text-xl text-teal-100 mb-6\">Sri Lanka&#x27;s trusted vehicle marketplace since 2019</p></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 bg-white\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center\"><div><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4\">Welcome to Rathagala.lk</h2><p class=\"text-slate-600 mb-4\">Welcome to Rathagala.lk, Sri Lanka’s trusted online vehicle classified website — the easiest way to buy and sell vehicles across the island.</p><p class=\"text-slate-600 mb-4\">We created Rathagala.lk with a simple vision: to make vehicle trading faster, safer, and more convenient for everyone. Whether you&#x27;re a car owner looking to sell, a buyer searching for your next ride, or a dealer promoting your stock — Rathagala.lk is your one-stop platform for all things automotive.</p><p class=\"text-slate-600\">We&#x27;ve designed the platform to make posting an ad take just a few minutes — no complicated forms, no hidden costs. Simply create a free account, upload your details, and your ad will be live for others to see.</p></div><div class=\"relative h-80 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-lg\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"text-center p-8\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-car h-16 w-16 mx-auto mb-4 text-teal-700\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M19 17h2c.6 0 1-.4 1-1v-3c0-.9-.7-1.7-1.5-1.9C18.7 10.6 16 10 16 10s-1.3-1.4-2.2-2.3c-.5-.4-1.1-.7-1.8-.7H5c-.6 0-1.1.4-1.4.9l-1.4 2.9A3.7 3.7 0 0 0 2 12v4c0 .6.4 1 1 1h2\"></path><circle cx=\"7\" cy=\"17\" r=\"2\"></circle><path d=\"M9 17h6\"></path><circle cx=\"17\" cy=\"17\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg><div class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-teal-900\">Rathagala.lk</div><p class=\"text-slate-600 mt-2\">186, Depanama, Pannipitiya</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 bg-slate-50\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4\">Our Mission</h2><p class=\"text-lg text-slate-600\">Our mission is to connect vehicle buyers and sellers through a reliable online marketplace where every listing is easy to post, easy to find, and easy to trust. We aim to become the most user-friendly classified website in Sri Lanka dedicated exclusively to vehicles.</p></div><div class=\"mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-6 text-center\">What You Can Find</h2><div class=\"text-center mb-6\"><p class=\"text-lg text-slate-600\">On Rathagala.lk, you can:</p></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border shadow-sm p-6 border-slate-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow text-center\"><div class=\"mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-teal-100 text-teal-700 mx-auto\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-car h-6 w-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M19 17h2c.6 0 1-.4 1-1v-3c0-.9-.7-1.7-1.5-1.9C18.7 10.6 16 10 16 10s-1.3-1.4-2.2-2.3c-.5-.4-1.1-.7-1.8-.7H5c-.6 0-1.1.4-1.4.9l-1.4 2.9A3.7 3.7 0 0 0 2 12v4c0 .6.4 1 1 1h2\"></path><circle cx=\"7\" cy=\"17\" r=\"2\"></circle><path d=\"M9 17h6\"></path><circle cx=\"17\" cy=\"17\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2\">Buy &amp; Sell Vehicles</h3><p class=\"text-slate-600 text-sm\">Cars, vans, jeeps, motorbikes, trucks, and buses</p></div><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border shadow-sm p-6 border-slate-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow text-center\"><div class=\"mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-teal-100 text-teal-700 mx-auto\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-award h-6 w-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6\"></circle></svg></div><h3 c